Maafkan aku.  Oke?

00:06:38.608 --> 00:06:39.732
Ayo sekarang.  Bangun.

00:06:40.357 --> 00:06:42.149
Cukup sekarang.  Ayo, bangun.

00:06:42.316 --> 00:06:43.232
Bangun..
- Sai.

00:06:43.399 --> 00:06:44.274
Bangun!

00:06:45.107 --> 00:06:46.149
Bangun.  Ayo.

00:06:46.357 --> 00:06:47.274
Ayah?

00:06:47.399 --> 00:06:48.399
Tolong bangun.

00:06:48.524 --> 00:06:49.441
Ayah, bangun.

00:06:49.649 --> 00:06:51.608
Bangun.  Ayo.  Dengarkan aku.
- Sai.

00:06:52.107 --> 00:06:54.441
Ayahmu telah meninggalkan kita.
- Bangun.

00:06:55.107 --> 00:06:56.191
Ayahmu tidak ada lagi.

00:06:57.773 --> 00:06:59.274
Bangun.  Saya tahu Anda akan.

00:06:59.815 --> 00:07:01.024
Bangun, ayolah.

00:07:01.316 --> 00:07:02.815
Bangun!  - Sai!

00:07:07.940 --> 00:07:12.065
Inspektur Joshi tidak ada lagi..

00:07:23.608 --> 00:07:25.316
Ya, saya akan tiba di sana dalam waktu setengah jam..
